               <sense xml:id="Dmain" xml:lang="la" source="#dillmann"> <gramGrp> <pos expand="Substantivum">subst.</pos> </gramGrp>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> tempus florum </t:quote></cit>, <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> ver </t:quote></cit>. In Aethiopia ver a fine Septembris mensis incipit, <lbl expand="videas">vid.</lbl> <ref cRef="Sx. Masc." loc="25 ">Sx. Masc. 25 </ref>Enc. (qui locus Lud. <lbl expand="lexicon">lex.</lbl> <lbl expand="columna">col.</lbl> 104 impressus est). In Bibliis <foreign xml:lang="grc">ὑετὸς ὄψιμος</foreign> (<cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> pluvia verna </t:quote></cit>) <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዝናመ፡ መፀው፡</foreign> versus est <ref cRef="Jer." loc="5,24">Jer. 5,24</ref>; <cb n="0229" xml:id="c0229"/> <ref cRef="Zach." loc="10,1">Zach. 10,1</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ያዘንም፡ ለክሙ፡ ጸዳየ፡ ወመፀወ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Joel " loc="2,23">Joel  2,23</ref>. Auctumnus et ver <foreign xml:lang="gez">ጸዳይ፡ ወመፀው፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Clem." loc="171">Clem. f. 171</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ክረምት፡ መፀው፡ ማእረር፡ ሐጋይ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Kuf." loc="2.">Kuf. 2.</ref> – Praeterea videas, quae sub <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሐጋይ፡</foreign> disputavimus. – <lbl expand="Vocabularium Aethiopicum, -a -a">Voc. Ae.</lbl>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">መፀው፡ ዘ፡ መዋዕለ፡ ጽጌያት፡</foreign>; <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> aliud </t:quote></cit>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘ፡ ዘመነ፡ በልግ፡</foreign>; <cit type="translation" xml:lang="la"><t:quote xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0"> aliud </t:quote></cit>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ዘመነ፡ ማእረር።</foreign> </sense>
               
